title: Piece Together Your Life
itunes:title: Piece Together Your Life
description:
Episode 375 - As much as we like to plan our lives out, sometimes we get a curveball thrown as us that was not part of the plan. What do you do now? How do we use that curveball as an integral part of the journey? Let's talk about it in this episode!
